OL,7,FResidents say they are 'deeply
OL,8,Fconcerned by the plans' and a petition
OL,9,Fcalling for the proposals to be
OL,10,Fscrapped, has gained more than 3,500
OL,11,Fsignatures.
OL,13,FOn the change.org page, organiser
OL,14,FKaren Russon said: "As residents of
OL,15,FMinster-On-Sea, we cherish our
OL,16,Fcommunity and its unique character.
