OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"We have been informed about a
OL,8,Fproposed immigration centre to house
OL,9,Fasylum seekers, expected to be
OL,10,Foperational by May 2024 at Ocean
OL,11,FHeights, Minster leas.
OL,13,F"This development deeply concerns us.
OL,15,F"Our beloved town is known for its
OL,16,Ftranquility and as a popular tourist
OL,17,Fhotspot.
