OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"The proposed site for the immigration
OL,8,Fcentre is next to the Little Oyster -
OL,9,Fa care home for vulnerable adults
OL,10,Fright in the heart of our community.
OL,12,F"We fear that this project will
OL,13,Fdisrupt our peaceful environment and
OL,14,Fpotentially pose risks to our
OL,15,Fvulnerable population.
