OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"Furthermore, it's important to
OL,8,Fconsider that introducing such a
OL,9,Ffacility in an area heavily reliant on
OL,10,Ftourism could negatively impact local
OL,11,Fbusinesses and employment rates
OL,12,F(source: Office for National
OL,13,FStatistics).
OL,15,F"We understand the need for asylum
OL,16,Fseeker housing but believe there are
OL,17,Fmore suitable locations which would
OL,18,Fnot disrupt established communities or
OL,19,Flocal economies.
