OL,7,FThe MP for Sittingbourne and Sheppey,
OL,8,FGordon Henderson said: "While I
OL,9,Funderstand that the KCC must follow
OL,10,Fthe instructions of the High Court
OL,11,Fjudgement, and that asylum seeking
OL,12,Fchildren must be properly cared for, I
OL,13,Fdo not believe Ocean Heights should be
OL,14,Fused for this purpose.
