OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"With that in mind I would like to
OL,8,Fassure my constituents on the Isle of
OL,9,FSheppey that, along with my colleague
OL,10,FAisha Cuthbert, I will fiercely oppose
OL,11,Fthis decision, for a number of
OL,12,Freasons, not least because the KCC
OL,13,Fhave just closed Blackburn Lodge,
OL,14,Fwhich was the only county funded adult
OL,15,Fsocial care home on the Isle of
OL,16,FSheppey.
