OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"For some time I have been pressing
OL,8,FKCC to provide alternative
OL,9,Faccommodation for adult social care
OL,10,Ffor people on the Island, but they
OL,11,Fsaid there were no suitable premises.
OL,12,FTo then use Ocean Heights, which is a
OL,13,Fnew, perfectly good, and empty care
OL,14,Fhome to house unaccompanied asylum
OL,15,Fseekers children, is rubbing salt into
OL,16,Fa very sore wound.
