OL,4,Cto house child asylum seekers in care
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"We are concerned about the decision
OL,8,Falso because Ocean Heights is situated
OL,9,Fin a holiday area on Sheppey, and is
OL,10,Fright next to the Little Oyster Care
OL,11,FHome that specialises in caring for
OL,12,Fpeople with learning disabilities,
OL,13,Fautism, physical disabilities and
OL,14,Fmental health conditions.
OL,16,F"I know many of my constituents will
OL,17,Fagree with Aisha and me, and I would
OL,18,Flike to assure them that I have made
OL,19,Fclear our views, in the strongest
OL,20,Fterms, to the leader of Kent County
OL,21,FCouncil.
