OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"At the same time, we are challenging
OL,8,Fthe Government through our own legal
OL,9,Fproceedings, to get the National
OL,10,FTransfer Scheme working to ensure that
OL,11,Fall Local Authorities in the UK take
OL,12,Fon their responsibility for the care
OL,13,Fof UAS Children. The Court made clear
OL,14,Fthat the Home Office must quickly
OL,15,Fimplement an effective and
OL,16,Fsuccessfully managed NTS to ensure
OL,17,Fthat Kent's Children's Services will
OL,18,Fnever again have to announce the
OL,19,Fposition of being so overwhelmed it
OL,20,Fcan no longer to take any new
OL,21,Freferrals of children into its care
OL,22,Fand Kent's services and taxpayers
OL,23,Funfairly burdened simply because of
OL,24,Four geography in relation to the
OL,25,Fshortest crossing route.
